column5: Does anyone know if these can be ordered online? Contact?
You can order over the phone from the MNR at 1-800-667-1940. I've been doing this for several years now and it works great.
Do you pay more for doing that?
No extra charge at all. And by using a credit card you get the most current exchange rate. I've found it to be very convenient.
